---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/lcg.css';
---

<Layout title="Services - LCG">
  <header>
    <nav>
      <div class="logo-group">
        <a href="/" class="logo">LC<span class="accent">G</span></a>
        <span class="logo-text">
          Lasana Cahaya <span class="accent">G</span>emilang
        </span>
      </div>
      <ul class="nav-menu">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services" class="active">Services</a></li>
        <li><a href="/insight">Insight</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero" style="min-height: 60vh;">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        <span class="word">Our</span>
        <span class="word">Services</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Comprehensive solutions across water infrastructure, energy transition, and global logistics.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <p>Strategic design and implementation across three core domains.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-2" style="gap: var(--space-3xl);">
        <!-- Water Supply Service -->
        <div class="card-feature">
          <h3>Water Supply Infrastructure</h3>
          <p>
            We design and optimize water infrastructure systems that bring clean, reliable water to communities. Our approach combines engineering excellence with human-centered design.
          </p>
          <h4 style="margin-top: var(--space-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-brand-primary);">Our expertise includes:</h4>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">✓ Water purification system design</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">✓ Distribution network optimization</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">✓ Sustainability impact assessment</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">✓ Community engagement frameworks</li>
            <li>✓ Maintenance and monitoring solutions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Energy Transition Service -->
        <div class="card-feature">
          <h3>Energy Transition Strategy</h3>
          <p>
            Moving beyond fossil fuels requires more than technology—it requires vision. We design strategic frameworks and interfaces that guide organizations through energy transformation.
          </p>
          <h4 style="margin-top: var(--space-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-brand-primary);">Our expertise includes:</h4>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">✓ Renewable energy system design</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">✓ Grid modernization strategies</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">✓ Stakeholder alignment frameworks</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">✓ Technology adoption roadmaps</li>
            <li>✓ Impact measurement and reporting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Logistic Network Service -->
        <div class="card-feature">
          <h3>Logistic Network Optimization</h3>
          <p>
            Global supply chains can be forces for good. We design and optimize logistics networks that maximize efficiency, transparency, and sustainability across every mile.
          </p>
          <h4 style="margin-top: var(--space-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-brand-primary);">Our expertise includes:</h4>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">✓ Supply chain architecture design</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">✓ Route optimization algorithms</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">✓ Visibility and tracking systems</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">✓ Sustainability integration</li>
            <li>✓ Partner enablement platforms</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background-color: var(--color-surface-secondary);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Our Approach</h2>
        <p>Every project follows the same rigorous process.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>01. Discover</h3>
          <p>We listen deeply. We ask hard questions. We understand your context, constraints, and true north.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>02. Design</h3>
          <p>We translate insights into strategy. We craft solutions that are both elegant and grounded in reality.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>03. Deliver</h3>
          <p>We build with precision. We iterate in the real world. We measure impact and optimize continuously.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>04. Sustain</h3>
          <p>We ensure your success extends beyond launch. We provide tools, training, and ongoing partnership.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Ready to Transform?</h2>
        <p>Let's discuss how we can partner on your most ambitious goals.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-content">
      <div class="footer-section">
        <h4>About LCG</h4>
        <p>Lasana Cahaya Gemilang is a creative platform dedicated to sustainable innovation and design excellence.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-section">
        <h4>Explore</h4>
        <p><a href="/services">Services</a></p>
        <p><a href="/insight">Insight</a></p>
        <p><a href="/about">About Us</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-section">
        <h4>Connect</h4>
        <p><a href="/contact">Contact</a></p>
        <p><a href="mailto:hello@lcg.creative">hello@lcg.creative</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Lasana Cahaya Gemilang. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  ul {
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
</style>
